<div class="avatar-image-container avatar-stock"><span dir="ltr"><a href="http://www.blogger.com/profile/01066366321468459399" rel="nofollow" onclick="" class="avatar-hovercard" id="av-65-01066366321468459399"><img src="http://img2.blogblog.com/img/b16-rounded.gif" width="16" height="16" alt="" title="Neverfox">

